[normal]has
[normal] learnt that to be effective, programmes must 
[normal]start
[normal] with people living with mental illness or epilepsy; and 
[normal]address illness, poverty and social exclusion of affected people and their families in a sustainable, holistic way
[normal].  
[normal]BasicNeeds has over the past thirteen years developed a unique Model which does just that, this Model is described below:
